      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Return the pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
